summary: A small house in Morrowind style.
descriptionHtml:
[size=2]A small house in Morrowind style. House is located near the Anga's Mill (On the west way to Windhelm). Look for map marker when you start game.

[/size][url=https://www.patreon.com/haemprojects][size=2][img]http://tesall.ru/uploads/imgs/pre_1535556014__11111.png[/img][/size][size=5]﻿[b]Support Haem Projects on Patreon![/b][/size][/url]﻿

[b][size=3]Features: [/size][/b]
[list]
[*][size=2]Design from Morrowind;[/size]
[*][size=2]All crafting stations;[/size]
[*][size=2]Weapon racks and mannequins;[/size]
[*][size=2]Common containers and bookshelves;[/size]
[*][size=2]Solstheim music in interiors;[/size]
[*][size=2]Fully navmeshed;[/size]
[*][size=2]Cleaned with Tes5edit.[/size]
[/list]
[b][size=3]Requirements: [/size][/b]
[size=2]All DLС [/size]

[b][size=3]Uninstall: [/size][/b]
[size=2]Before uninstalling mod empty all containers and exit interior cell. [/size]

[center][youtube]iAgsp9DYsoo[/youtube][youtube]TXLCfIygDtA[/youtube][/center]

[size=3][b]Third Party Content:[/b][/size]
[size=2]Some models for exterior and interior taken from public build of Skywind. Models were corrected and reconfigured by us.[/size]
